# UPGRADE 2: INVINCIBILITY, COST: 3x Tier 3 Red Gems		
					
on right click:
	name of player's tool is "&9Water Staff &8| &bWater Shield &8[&cðŸ’ŽðŸ’ŽðŸ’ŽðŸ’ŽðŸ’Ž&8]":
		if difference between now and {WATERSHIELDNEW.%player's uuid%.WATERSHIELDNEW.lastUsed} is less than 90 seconds:
			cancel event
			message "&8[&câœ–&8] &cWater Shield is on cooldown! &8(%difference between {WATERSHIELDNEW.%player's uuid%.WATERSHIELDNEW.lastUsed} and (90 seconds before now)%)" to player
		else:
			set {WATERSHIELDNEW.%player's uuid%.WATERSHIELDNEW.lastUsed} to now
